data.title: Mahabub
data.text: A great teacher to teach English. He is keeping students busy as much as possible. Sometime students fail to complete his homework.

data.title: Paresh
data.text: All students like him. Some students doesn't do their home work at all. But the teacher is above of them. He is happy for doing nothing.

data.title: Janid
data.text: He is very active for his class. He always try to show something to his student but sometimes it isn't possible for him to do that.
